parameters: I'm sorry... It must smell bad, right?
I'm sorry... It's because I got caught...
I'm the same... Besides, I'm fine...
Ahaha... Did Masamune-kun believe it too...?

Men tend to be happy when they get that kind of
reaction...

Thanks to that, he looked satisfied and went
somewhere...
...So that's how it was... I was deceived too.
The plan was a great success, huh...

Now... all that's left is to free Masamune-kun
from the prison... but it seems like my body still
won't move...

Take a little more rest, it'll be fine. I'll think
of a way to escape too.
Next... I will definitely win, you know.

Of course... in the end, we will be the ones to
emerge victorious.

(It's okay... Amelia is still the same Amelia I
know...)
...I'm sorry... for not being able to help...
Next... I will be the one to help.
(The ritual... the black mass has begun...)
(However, I know exactly who the culprit is)
